info.name: WeSeeDoDirect-WeSeeDo
info.description:
WeSeeDo Direct API allows you to set up a video communication channel between people by sending an SMS with a link to the meeting. This API specification is for version 2 of the API.

### Key highlights

- **Sandbox:** Full-fledged capabilities.
- **Security:** HTTPS, OAuth, Rate limit.
- **Versioning:** Supports version-less API, version tight. If no version is provided (in the header) it defaults to latest version.
    

---

## [KPN Developer](https://developer.kpn.com/)  
[Getting Started](https://developer.kpn.com/getting-started)

---

Contact Support:  
Name: API Support  
Email: [api_developer@kpn.com](mailto:api_developer@kpn.com)
